{"tid":1886671,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎》彭博：全球已進入「歷史性供應鏈斷鏈」時期","createTime":"2020-02-19T05:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T00:39:17.000Z","uid":141151,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"23e89eab8d7efb47d156f38a83c43177a6e93bfd","tid":1886671,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎》彭博：全球已進入「歷史性供應鏈斷鏈」時期<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3069967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3069967&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=29ce3587\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3069967&h=d8cfb6e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3069967</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕國際貿易90％仰賴海運，而中國又是海運大國，但自武漢肺炎疫情爆發後，已有數十艘滿載中國貨物的船班被取消，這對全球供應鏈的影響是世界性的，因此《彭博》在報導中形容：未來人們回顧2020年2月，將是一段歷史性的供應鏈斷鏈的時代。<br />\n<br />\n中國海運停滯造成的影響可說是「貨出不去還進不來」，如中國製造的玩具、精品、平板等產品，沒有辦法交付到買家手上，甚至造成整個產業的斷鏈，例如遠在天邊、位於塞爾維亞的飛雅特克萊斯勒（FCA）汽車工廠，已因為缺乏來自中國的零組件而暫時關閉。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，石油、天然氣、煤炭、鐵礦等資源都無法輸送至中國，西非、中南美、歐洲北海都預期需求減弱，已有中國買家向沙烏地阿拉伯請求減供原油，並以「不可抗力」為由請求減供天然氣，造成油輪漂浮在海上，而世界最大天然氣生產國卡達，近期外海出現了12艘空空如也的天然氣載運船。<br />\n<br />\n報導也提到，由於有大量空貨輪停泊在中國出不去，也連帶影響其它國家出口；海運諮詢機構Sea Intelligence執行長墨菲（Alan Murphy）估計，目前約有60萬個20呎標準貨櫃被困在中國無法使用，加拿大豆類協會（Pulse Canada）發言人就表示，現在在加拿大已越來越難找到空貨櫃了。<br />\n<br />\n墨菲估計，「貨出不去」的結果，估計各海運公司每週損失的金額高達6億美元，除非疫情能在未來幾週以內消退，不然最好的方法可能是讓業務閒置直到疫情結束為止。"},{"pid":"251b01664db631c6b05a7e4ce51756e2cf2d85fe","tid":1886671,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"支爆冚球鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46345e8af0a001421eee9d956ec1d1a2e3265561","tid":1886671,"uid":47311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:11:39.000Z","msg":"急不及待想玩玩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6144784c38dfabe8b1783edc235155f640721575","tid":1886671,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:14:11.000Z","msg":"幫手推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「行動post」Twitter師全面進場 推到美國搞Youtube！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fbzANS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fbzANS</a>"},{"pid":"ad762645aed8cb047c5b04b91efd1e0eaa7d07e9","tid":1886671,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"251b01664db631c6b05a7e4ce51756e2cf2d85fe","tid":1886671,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"支爆冚球鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:15:36.000Z","msg":"聽日去砌機先<br />\n唔係無板了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae3042885f9caab5faffa897c9cba7bc78b84af","tid":1886671,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:21:38.000Z","msg":"預視到嘅未來<br />\n<br />\n新推出嘅iPhone會出貨慢左"},{"pid":"0635310687617c1095827e2c099c9ce0b1799f41","tid":1886671,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f50f40c37f9f9e8d116c20feff89b554540b92","tid":1886671,"uid":204039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T18:38:47.000Z","msg":"美國提大家<br />\n再設廠唔好去中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18861d74d5e13f55bfc2c4ce7a810eb16080d3da","tid":1886671,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T18:40:19.000Z","msg":"Trump一早提左大家<br />\n有聽佢話就大勝"},{